Text: I am glad to see you are back Goodfilms, you upload good films and that is..... good......... :)
Thanks :) not sure if i'm actually back though. we'll see. very limited bandwidth these days.

either way, you were missed..

the timing is rather appropriate as well.. as the powers that be finally saw fit to remove the often abused plus/minus quality mechanism that was the bane of your existence so relentlessly
The original seeder seems to have abandoned this, it is stuck at 92.8% highest peer.
Some patience may be required on this one.
